---
import Panel from './Panel.astro';
---

<Panel title="MTX ECOSYSTEM" class="mtx-panel">
  <div class="panel-text">
    <strong>MTX</strong> is the key token powering Matrix-Hub.<br>
    Earn, spend, burn, and lock MTX to unlock features, access premium tools, and participate in the Casino.
  </div>
  
  <ul class="mtx-features">
    <li><span class="feature-label">Earn MTX:</span> Usage milestones, bug reports, GitHub actions, community testing</li>
    <li><span class="feature-label">Spend MTX:</span> Premium tools, priority execution, experimental modules, Casino games</li>
    <li><span class="feature-label">Burn MTX:</span> A % of premium spending is burned to keep supply healthy</li>
    <li><span class="feature-label">Lock MTX:</span> Stake MTX for tier access, unlock after a set period</li>
    <li><span class="feature-label">Casino:</span> Play slots, blackjack, roulette to win or spend MTX</li>
  </ul>
  
  <div class="panel-text mtx-summary">
    MTX is useful, accessible, and designed for sustainable growthâ€”no hype cycles required.
  </div>
  
  <div class="mtx-links">
    <h4 style="color:var(--theme-primary); margin-bottom: 10px;">Learn More About MTX:</h4>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="/docs/MTX_Whitepaper.md" target="_blank">MTX Whitepaper</a></li>
      <li><a href="/docs/MTX_Tokenomics.md" target="_blank">MTX Tokenomics</a></li>
      <li><a href="/docs/MTX_DAO_Governance.md" target="_blank">DAO Governance</a></li>
      <li><a href="/docs/MTX_Disclaimer.md" target="_blank">Disclaimer</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</Panel>

<style>
  .mtx-panel {
    --matrix-pulse-color: var(--theme-border);
    margin: 30px auto;
    max-width: 900px;
    border: 2px solid var(--theme-border);
    box-shadow: 0 0 24px var(--theme-glow);
  }
  
  .mtx-features {
    margin: 18px 0 0 20px;
    font-size: 1.08rem;
    color: var(--theme-text);
  }
  
  .mtx-features li {
    margin: 8px 0;
  }
  
  .feature-label {
    color: var(--theme-primary);
    font-weight: bold;
  }
  
  .mtx-summary {
    margin-top: 18px;
    color: var(--theme-secondary);
    font-size: 1.08rem;
  }
  
  .mtx-links {
    margin-top: 24px;
  }
  
  .mtx-links ul {
    margin-left: 20px;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }
  
  .mtx-links li {
    margin: 8px 0;
  }
  
  .mtx-links a {
    color: var(--theme-primary);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  
  .mtx-links a:hover {
    color: var(--theme-secondary);
    text-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--theme-glow);
  }
</style>
